inputs.description: A collection of arguments for invoking getResource.

arn.description: ARN of the resource, an S3 path.

outputs.description: A collection of values returned by getResource.

id.description: The provider-assigned unique ID for this managed resource.

lastModified.description: Date and time the resource was last modified in [RFC 3339 format](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3339#section-5.8).

roleArn.description: Role that the resource was registered with.
